<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-turns">take turns</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>轮流；依次：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>took turns</strong> ( <strong>in</strong> ) <strong>driving</strong>. 
他们轮流开车。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>take turns to do</strong> the housework. 
我们轮流做家务。</p></div></div>